message.body: Hey is everything ok with u.
Yeah. So far. Moving cars now and I'll prolly have to help my neighbors cut down a fallen tree in a minute but things are relatively calm at the moment. How are you guys?
Ok cool. Stay safe . I'm at work n may not b able to leave boys n Lou are safe at home watching the rain fall.
Don't worry, I'm strapped. You be safe too. Save some lives over there.
